comments.body: We will wait for more... :)
Thanks!  Going through all my notebooks has inspired me to want to draw more, though I may have to wait until it isn't below zero out to get out and do field sketches again.
I actually colored this by wiping the corresponding plant parts on the drawing.  The leaf color has remained, though the flower color hasn't really.
Nice sketch.
thanks!  I'm glad people like the sketches I uploaded.  I've exhausted my old notebooks so no more until I have time to draw new ones (which won't happen when it is so cold)
That is very pretty :) !
I can't believe I haven't iNaturalisted Gleason Brook yet except for these sketches! Definitely a target for spring ephemerals soon.
